<Section id={"intro"} title={"1. Tб»•ng quan opencode"} themeTag={"Intro"}>
  <p>
    <strong>opencode</strong> lГ  mб»ҷt AI coding agent open-source chбәЎy trГӘn terminal,
    IDE, vГ  desktop. Repo
    <a href="https://github.com/anomalyco/opencode">anomalyco/opencode</a> lГ  fork
    chГӯnh cб»§a
    <code>sst/opencode</code> vб»ӣi rбәҘt nhiб»Ғu package: core agent (<code
      >packages/opencode</code
    >), desktop app (Tauri + Electron), web console, plugin SDK, infrastructure
    (SST), v.v.
  </p>
  <p>
    BГЎo cГЎo nГ y chб»ү tбәӯp trung vГ o <strong>harness cб»§a core agent</strong> вҖ” phбә§n "scaffolding"
    xoay quanh LLM call Д‘б»ғ biбәҝn mб»ҷt model trбә§n thГ nh mб»ҷt coding agent hoбәЎt Д‘б»ҷng Д‘Ж°б»Јc.
    Scope bao gб»“m 6 subsystem chГӯnh:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <code>session/</code> вҖ” agent loop, streaming processor, compaction, retry
    </li>
    <li>
      <code>tool/</code> вҖ” tool registry, tool implementations, truncation
    </li>
    <li>
      <code>provider/</code> вҖ” abstraction cho 20+ LLM providers, message transformation,
      error classification
    </li>
    <li><code>permission/</code> вҖ” permission engine vб»ӣi wildcard + arity</li>
    <li>
      <code>agent/</code> вҖ” agent definitions (build, plan, custom subagents)
    </li>
    <li><code>mcp/</code>, <code>plugin/</code> вҖ” extension points</li>
  </ul>
  <Subheading level="h3" id="what-is-harness" text="Harness lГ  gГ¬?" />
  <p>
    Cб»ҷng Д‘б»“ng coding-agent Д‘ang dбә§n dГ№ng thuбәӯt ngб»Ҝ "harness" nhЖ° mб»ҷt shorthand
    cho
    <em>tбәҘt cбәЈ nhб»Ҝng gГ¬ khГҙng phбәЈi model</em> вҖ” tб»©c lГ : <strong
      >Agent = Model + Harness</strong
    >. Harness engineering lГ  subset cб»§a context engineering, xoay quanh viб»Үc
    quбәЈn lГҪ context window, tool orchestration, state persistence, error
    recovery, verification, safety, vГ  lifecycle.
  </p>
  <Callout type="info">
    <p>
      <strong>Tham khбәЈo vб»Ғ khГЎi niб»Үm harness:</strong>
      Martin Fowler вҖ” <a
