        >Harness engineering for coding agent users</a
      >
      В· OpenAI вҖ” <a href="https://openai.com/index/harness-engineering/"
        >Harness engineering: leveraging Codex in an agent-first world</a
      >
      В· HumanLayer вҖ” <a
        href="https://www.humanlayer.dev/blog/skill-issue-harness-engineering-for-coding-agents"
        >Skill Issue: Harness Engineering for Coding Agents</a
      >
      В· Avi Chawla вҖ” <a
        href="https://blog.dailydoseofds.com/p/the-anatomy-of-an-agent-harness"
